NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::LogBuild - Add build information file (build.log)

VERSION
    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
    In your dist.ini:

      [LogBuild]

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin generates a "build.log" file containing build information
    (like the list of loaded plugins and their versions) to aid in
    debugging.

FUNCTIONS
    None are exported by default, but they are exportable.

SEE ALSO
    Dist::Zilla

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Dist-Zilla-Plugin-LogBuild>.

SOURCE
